{"name": "United Food Bank of Plant City", "alternate_name": "", "description": "Please make Appointment on website https://calendly.com/ufbnewclients/new?month=2024-10 before reaching to pantry for sign up
Eligibility is based on a person’s area of residence. Please see below for the zip codes we serve.  

**Zip Codes we service:**

* Brandon: 33510, 33511
* Dover: 33527
* Dover/Sydney: 33587
* Lithia: 33547
* Plant City  33563, 33564, 33565, 33566, 33567
* Riverview: 33569
* Seffner: 33584
* Thonotosassa: 33592
* Valrico 33594, 33596
**ALL NEW CLIENTS MUST ARRIVE 30 MINUTES PRIOR TO CLOSE TO BE ABLE TO SIGN UP.**

**DOCUMENTS REQUIRED TO RECEIVE ASSISTANCE ARE:**
* Current Photo Id (Driver’s license or state ID)
* Current proof of address in the main account holder’s name
Examples include(not limited to): recent TECO and Utility bills, Access or Social Security mailed documents

Clients can visit every two weeks
Questions please contact the office (813) 764-0625 ext. 5
